comments: Zeller (CHA) steps into the lane prior to the release of the free throw.
Washington (CHI) makes contact with Markkanen's (CHI) arm that affects his play at the basket.
Zeller (CHA) receives the pass and takes two legal steps after the gather.
Bridges (CHA) briefly places his arms around Carter Jr. (CHI) and the two players engage and disengage.
Carter Jr. (CHI) lifts his pivot before the release of his dribble.
Satoransky (CHI) and Graham (CHA) engage and disengage prior to the inbound pass.
LaVine (CHI) makes marginal contact with Bridges (CHA) during the screen.
Graham (CHA) makes marginal contact with Markkanen's (CHI) arm that does not affect Markkanen's ability to catch the pass.
Zeller (CHA) jumps into Markkanen's (CHI) body and affects his play at the basket.
Zeller (CHA) extends two arms and pushes Satoransky (CHI) during the screen.
Porter Jr. (CHI) makes marginal contact to Graham (CHA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Zeller (CHA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in the path of LaVine (CHI).
Porter Jr. (CHI) briefly places his hand on Bacon's (CHA) arm that does not affect his FOM.
Porter Jr. (CHI) makes contact to Graham's arm (CHA) that affects his ability to gather the ball.
Carter Jr. (CH) makes contact with the ball, but also with Zeller (CHA) that affects his SQBR.
Bacon (CHA) makes body contact to Markkanen (CHI) during his drive that affects his SQBR.
Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact with Bacon (CHA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Markkanen (CHI) makes contact to Graham's arm (CHA) that affects his SQBR.
Williams (CHA) briefly places a forearm to the front of LaVine (CHI) but the contact is marginal.
LaVine (CHI) wraps Graham (CHA) and affects his FOM.
Rozier (CHA) makes incidental contact with LaVine (CHI).
There is no conclusive angle to determine if Markkanen (CHI) makes contact with Bacon (CHA).
